review: Dr Shylaja Reddy was very helpful. She explained the problems and treatment options patiently. I’m very happy with the result.

Doctors were very friendly and cooperative. I met with an accident and had my front teeth broken. Doctors attended my case immediately andbhad done timely treatment and restored my traumatised teeth with crowns which are aesthetically very pleasing. I am very impressed with my treatment and the doctors.
The doctor was pretty comforting. And told everything in detail regarding the process and maintenance before and after tooth removed. Overall it was good experience

review:
I am visited Dr. M. Venkat Reddy at KJS dental Hospital, AS Rao Nagar. I am very satisfied with the advise given by the doctors and friendly nature of the staff and doctors turn up time to the patient. They listened all the queries raised by me and explained in very professional manner to all my concerns. One can visit this dental hospital for oral screening and other allied dental disciplines. Thanks to Dr. M. Venkat Reddy and his team.
Thanks and Regards,
Dr. Uma Mahesh Y; MSc., Ph.D.

We have committed to consulting with Dr. Venkat Reddy based on the user reviews. While we approach the hospital, the receptionist told that Mr. Venkat Reddy is not available in the hospital and alternative doctor is available for consulting, more over Mr. Venkat Reddy will not available all times. The treat was not satisfied and do not recommend further to any one
